<p>'In the beginning, Dr Laubscher put me on this super greens powder which has about 50 ingredients that amplify and boost each other as a sort of multi-vitamin and mineral,' Elle said.</p>

<p>'She also gave me a lot of different pills and a schedule as to when to take them.'</p>

<p>Within a week, the supermodel returned to Dr Laubscher and reported on the incredible progress:</p>

<p>'I was a completely different woman,' Elle recalled.</p>

<p>'I had lost weight, I was vibrant, my hair, skin and nails were glowing, and I said I couldn't believe the changes. But I told her the only thing I wanted was to not be taking all these pills all day.</p>

<p>'I said to her: "Can you put it all together in one thing that I can take first thing in the morning?"'</p>

<p>This was the original formulation for Elle's Welleco business and her Super Elixir powder.</p>

<p>This is a daily health supplement formulated using a combination of 40 naturally derived ingredients, including wholefoods, herbal extracts, vitamins, minerals and probiotics.</p>

<p>The powder was made by Elle and Dr Simone Laubscher, and now sells across the world.</p>

<p>Within a week, the model (pictured) said she had lost weight, and her hair, skin and nails were glowing - but she didn't want to keep taking multiple supplements daily</p>

<p>When it comes to Elle's other well-being secrets, the model said she loves early nights, ocean swims and bike rides.</p>

<p>'I typically get up early and do all my Welleco meetings on Zoom, before I go for a swim or a bike ride in the afternoon,' she said. </p>

<p>The 56-year-old also meditates for just 15 minutes each day, and makes sure she drinks between two and three litres of water.</p>

<p>Finally, while she never prioritised sleep when her kids were young, Elle said she now never gets less than seven hours sleep.  </p>

<ol>
<li>Hydrate: 'My wellness routine starts with two teaspoons of Welleco's Super Elixir every morning in cold spring water, or coconut water for extra hydration,' Elle said.</li>
</ol>

<p>Elle's golden health rules include adequate hydration and good sleep</p>

<ol start="2">
<li><p>Get active: Elle makes sure she does 45 minutes of fitness every single day, whether that's walking, running, swimming or yoga. She especially loves paddle boarding, hiking, biking and water skiing.</p></li>
